name: Lieutenant Williams (V)
Lore: 'Pilot of the Radiant VII. Was personally requested by Captain Madakor to assist in the transportation of the Jedi ambassadors.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Radiant VII, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. During battle at a system, if about to draw a battle destiny here, may instead draw two and choose one; if at opponent''s system, may take other destiny into hand.',
